channel.title: 2 Guys 1 Cup AFL Podcast
channel.description: Wil Anderson and Charlie Clausen look at the week in footy (sort of).

item.title: Round 10, 2022 - Manpower Bailey, Touk’s Guns, The Big Dog
item.description: The Dog’ goal kicking woes, the Tigers still got that Entourage bond, 15 nuggets is not a lot.

item.title: Round 9, 2022 - Ross' Pumpkin Sledge, Becoming Touk, Cogs Can't Cook
item.description: We put the focus on QLD footy, Gerard Healy stumbles through a coffee gag and special guest Alex Williams drop by to farewell Leon Cameron.

item.title: Round 8, 2022 - BT’s Donkey Kick, Fake Kanes, Flying Pale 2-Meter Peter
item.description: The Dogs had a shocker, but the commentary was worse, Kane’s got some competetition, Two-Metre Peter gets his own song.

item.title: Round 7, 2022 - Lace Up Gurnsey, Cheeky Gack, Ball Magnet Mitchell
item.description: Wil almost didn’t make the recording, Kane tries to stay relevant, Tom Mitchell plays Wil back into form.

item.title: Round 6, 2022: Cheeky Jack, Gresh’s Nike Brows, Robbo’s Back
item.description: The Pies resident pest makes Kane eat his words, a listener reveals the secret behind Gresh’s eyebrows, Robbo’s back to his incomprehensible best on AFL 360.

item.title: Round 5, 2022: Robocox, Gresh’s Waxed Brows, Fancying Freo
item.description:
Can Mason Cox become the most armoured player in the game?
The Lions Get Joe.
Dayne Zorko gives away nothing in his Pocket Profile.

item.title: Round 4, 2022 - Zac/Jack, Blue Sunday, Make Parents Umpire
item.description: Are the Saints building to a huge St Killing Me? One clanger sums up Port’s season. Home ground advantage should mean tougher umpires.

item.title: Round 3, 2022 - Trolling The Twerp, Wil Goes Whack, Bowey Not A Showey
item.description: The guys dissect Round 3 of the 2022 AFL Season. Kane Cornes is the ultimate contrarian. What are the AFL's most difficult names to pronounce? Pocket Player Profile

item.title: Round 2, 2022 - Bevo’s Bottom Bottom Boys, Buddy 1000 COVID-19, The Plat Ratten
item.description: The guys dissect Round 2 of the 2022 AFL Season. Is 0-2 a recipe for finals? Why spreading ashes on a footy oval is a bad idea. Cindy loves Lois & Clark. Adam Spencer chats Buddy's 100th.

item.title: Round 1, 2022 - Give Kane a Gong, Party Boy Callum, El Chorizo Returns
item.description:
The guys recap Round 1 of 2022.
It was a great round for anyone who doesn't have to talk about footy on a podcast, with the Dogs and the Saints off to bad starts. Kane Cornes is back being a twerp and everyone's favourite segment, the Pocket Profile Pocket returns for 2022.

item.title: 2022 - Season Preview
item.description: Wil & Charlie are back for the 2022 AFL season, and as usual, they're doing their start of year tradition... naming the coaches, captains and best and fairest players from each club in the competition!
